some of them have bugs/enforcerhits that lead sooner or
later to a crash (at least on Amithlon).
E.g. the library providing "sound", "loadsound", "period" etc.
is killing AHI if the Paula driver is running even if the commands
are never used.

I have programs written that have this problems and some not.
So I wanted to find out which of the libs cause this enforcer hits
to warn about this libs but it is simply far to much work. So is there
any possibility to find out which libs are used ? Maybe it is possible to do
it
in the way Newtypes are displayed just in a window listing
all used Libs ? This would be very helpful.

Thanks for any comments about that,

Thilo

